From history-making wins, unexpected performances and awkward interviews, it was a big night at the Oscars on Sunday.  And after the ceremony was all wrapped up, there was the small matter of the after party.  This year. the official bash was once again held by Vanity Fair, with Radhika Jones on hosting duties.  Many of those who were in attendance at the Oscars hot-footed it down the road to the Wallis Annenberg Center for the Performing Arts in Beverly Hills – with many also opting for an outfit change in between the ’dos. Take a look at all the red carpet snaps below...